<br>
To get off you either click the buff off or type /dismount.<br>
To get on you right click the bridle.<br>
<br>
There is no way to get rid of the graphic other than turning off luclin and horse models for your race.  Its not that bad, just live with it.  Horse head with regen &gt; no horse.<br>
<br>
Horse is outdoor buff.  If you can sow there you can horse there.<br>
<br>
While on a horse you eat food and drink faster.  Either force feed yourself summoned food to prevent yourself from eating the good stuff, get meta3 to help there, or just buy food more often. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><br>
